{
  "stem": "12447.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they opened the hoses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And anybody getting up, they would shoot, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they knew that everybody was dehydrated, and everybody's going to get up and run for water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they, they just played a game with us, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They poured the water on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whoever went up to get a-- to get-- to get wet or something was shot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some of the water sprayed over us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the, the, the hoses weren't actually reaching the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was just a game.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they did that game.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they killed some more people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by noontime, there was a rumor that they're going to take everybody out, and they're going to take us to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everybody got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody lined up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we started to walk to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time, the coat-- I mean, the suit that my mother dressed me actually was so beneficial to me because she told me that I should take it off now.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So when I got off this dirty, wet suit from blood, I had a clean change of clothes underneath.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this saved my life, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because walking toward the railroad station, my father told me that I have to run away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have to make my way out of the situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have to be the survivor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] Of course, I didn't want to listen to that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't want to separate from my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I said, I'm not going to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm going to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we knew that we're probably going to Treblinka because we heard rumors of Treblinka, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And nobody ever came from there to tell what happened there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we knew it was the end of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
